          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <node refid="T6" role="Increase"/>
          <node refid="T5" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">5</infon>
        <offset>844</offset>
        <text>EPM-NM and motile EPL showed the highest and lowest NPQ, respectively, with EPM-M showing intermediate values.
</text>
